						               													<description>Harter Tobak is a German card game by Simon &amp;amp; Jan where you have to fill in the blanks and build card combinations.&amp;#10;The standard version of it launched in 2014,  the Mobbing Edition. In the end of 2018 the Mobbing Edition has been released.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The 2014 version was very comparable to cards against humanity individualized by a whole bunch of special cards that changed the game mechanisms mid-game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The so called Mobbing Edition from 2018 brought in a very unique focus by specializing on bullying the people playing this game. In every round there is one bully and one bullying victim. The card combinations that need to be created have the goal to hit the chosen bullying victim.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
